mixin hero(heroLogo)
  div(class="text-center hero")
    img(
      class="mb-3 app-logo"
      src=heroLogo
      alt="Pug logo"
      width="120"
    )
    h1(class="mb-4") Express Sample Project
    p(class="lead")
      | This is a sample application that demonstrates an authentication flow for a web app, using&nbsp;
      a(
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        href="https://expressjs.com/"
      ) Express

